Mode: `local` (Compose data services only ‚Äî no public hosts, no GitOps)

To upgrade to `full` mode (Cloudflare Tunnel + k3s + ArgoCD + Tekton):

1. set `OUTPOST_MODE=full` in `.env`
2. fill `ROOT_DOMAIN`, `CF_TUNNEL_TOKEN`, `GIT_USER`, `GIT_TOKEN`, `MANIFEST_REPO_URL`
3. re-run `bash bootstrap.sh`

