## 4. Manticore Search 7.4.6 (standalone)

- HTTP/JSON API: `http://localhost:9308`
- MySQL wire   : `mysql -h127.0.0.1 -P9306`
- Binary / future replication slot: `localhost:9312`
- Auth: none (standalone has no built-in auth)
- Replication hook: see `core/compose/manticore/README.md`

```bash
# Health probe
curl http://localhost:9308/

# Open a SQL shell
mysql -h127.0.0.1 -P9306 -e 'SHOW STATUS'
```

